node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be an image of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez Does dropshipping still work in 2021? Over the last 3 years, I've generated over $3M in sales. Here's my blueprint to becoming a profitable dropshipper in 2021.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be an image of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez First off, here's how my dropshipping journey started. In college, got introduced to entrepreneurship and started 4 different dropshipping businesses. I ended up failing at all of them and found myself $10,000 in debt...'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be an image of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez I had to get a job and was so close to quitting until unti came across high ticket dropshipping. For the next 8 months, worked 12 hours a day and started making $10k/ month profit. And by now I've generated over $3M in sales. So here's the blueprint.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez 1. Open your LLC High ticket e-commerce is a legitimate business. Before you can close a supplier you need an LLC, a resale certificate, and a Tax ID.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be an image of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez 2. Find products & suppliers I don't sell cheap China products. only sell high-quality high ticket products from US suppliers. Find products worth AT LEAST $500 and suppliers that have less than 10 retailers. Wayfair is a great place to start.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez 3. Create your demo site Create a demo store and list your first demo products. The sole purpose of this is to show suppliers what the store is going to look like so you have a better chance at closing them.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be an image of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez 4. Close suppliers Just like with every other business model you need to know how to sell. Once you find potential suppliers get them on the phone. What helped me close them is to think big and be confident.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be an image of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez 5. Set up Google Ads I choose Google Ads over Facebook Ads because only want to offer my products to people who are already looking for them. Note: You won't get rich after your first Ad. It's all about testing until you find a winner.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez 6. Scale & Automate Hire employees that can take care of customer service and do the day-to- day tasks so you can focus on growing the business and creating your freedom.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 16, 2021 tagging @themichaelopez. May be an image of text that says 'Mikey Lopez @themichaelopez This is how you can build a profitable dropshipping business in 2021. I'm not rich by any means, but I can wake up and do whatever the hell want knowing my money is coming in. If you want more dropshipping tips like that, drop me a follow.'.
